{"itemid":1267,"subject":"More Wild Cards Goodness","event":"Here's a fanfare for all of you Wild Cards fans out there.\r\n\r\nThere's a brand new, never-before-published Wild Cards story just up on Tor.Com.\r\n\r\nThis one was penned by Cherie Priest.  It's called \"The Button Man and the Murder Tree.\"\r\n\r\nThe 'cover art' by the amazing John Picacio.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/167127/167127_300.jpg\" alt=\"full_buttonman\" title=\"full_buttonman\" width=\"266\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nThis one is a sort of 'origin story' for Cherie's Button Man character, last seen in FORT FREAK.\r\n\r\nYou can read it here:\r\nhttp://www.tor.com/stories/2013/05/the-button-man-and-the-murder-tree\r\n\r\nMore Wild Cards coming on Tor.com... and of course on the shelves of your local bookshop.","ditemid":324444,"eventtime":"2013-05-15 12:36:00","props":{"current_location":"Santa Fe","taglist":"tor, wild cards, sf","current_moodid":125,"commentalter":1371843008,"opt_lockcomments":1,"picture_keyword":"lohengrin","opt_screening":"F","personifi_tags":"nterms:yes","interface":"web","revnum":1,"revtime":1371843576},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2013-05-15 18:36:22","anum":92,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/324444.html","event_timestamp":1368621360,"reply_count":4,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/116131088/45519721","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/324444.html?thread=17744988#t17744988","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/324444.html?thread=17744988#t17744988","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/324444.html?thread=17744988#t17744988","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"superscienceser","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://superscienceser.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":17744988,"talkid":69316,"thread_url":"http: